reviewText: The sea planes of WWII are amazing!! I have a collection of over 300 WWII plastic model kit's (in 1/48 scale), and the sea planes are really cool!! this program is about those really cool kit's, that I have!! It's History that all can enjoy!! and to my Fans....I am Nimrod Jones!! I rate this a "Popcorn" movie/documentary....playing in homes all across Amazons' Planet, as of now...of course!!
